2266b2c434098be29ed459d26c3aa","tid":317911,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面嗰班話好人好者唔怕自已比mon 嘅簡直係弱智&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n只要有你足夠嘅data, 已經可以洗你腦！<br />\n一個例子，你上YouTube佢按係你嘅record 黎recommend 啲片，但如果佢有政治目的，只係recommend啲想你支持中共or 愛國嘅片呢？耳濡目染下，得好少人仍然可以保持independent mind <br />\n依家佢收集嘅仲要係你全面嘅data。<br />\n你一有data 比佢就可以analysis 到你係咪佢要嘅target，再analysis點洗你腦好。<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩十幾億人，邊有多對眼會認真睇你，係，就係唔想認真睇你，所以會由algorithm代勞。<br />\n<br />\n如果你咁都覺得冇所謂嘅，我冇嘢講。</blockquote><br />\n中國人仲有大部分香港人選擇科技產品, 個考慮係 實用性=價錢&gt;售後服務&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;私隱<br />\n歐美就掉番轉 私隱&gt;實用=服務&gt;價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a92c03887cbc7a93371c03d3bc40fde39713a62","tid":317911,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:21:01.000Z","msg":"美國一早有臉容識別付款<br />\n你一入舖就根據你習慣整飲品同付款<br />\n你行到櫃檯就攞飲品就走<br />\n但外國重視私穩最後都係一個小區實驗<br />\n流行唔到"},{"pid":"706799290cab79189c84033d60dc3db4da8cd019","tid":317911,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那為咗監視支那人仲可以推幾多「服務」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我第一反應就是這個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407649534d48807e950ecafeca6c517262dd93b0","tid":317911,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:23:57.000Z","msg":"在隔離的中國大陸，私隱不算甚麼！"},{"pid":"fef07735edc097a4e4aaa2ea851d1d4640c5dea0","tid":317911,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:25:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那為咗監視支那人仲可以推幾多「服務」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我第一反應就是這個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國既政治特性令到佢注定係呢個大數據時代係實用科技上行得最前 (但理論研究上美國仍然會係最前)"},{"pid":"ae00c80f3d43b79b012e75bbbab62c49875e34e0","tid":317911,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"你會對香港班不思進取商家佬又愛又恨，好在佢地思想冇咁前衛，我唔想飲杯野都被人影相，仲要係立體輪廓數據都俾埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f92d4a8925ef2a8a6edc58f4fd359fb4c778cb","tid":317911,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"呢個技術係十幾年前已經有<br />\n不過係CIA用黎追蹤恐怖分子/罪犯用<br />\nlinkup所有cctv 然後電腦就會不斷screening去搵"},{"pid":"3c032e782d6358a27989ea6d897882d3abd6e5b1","tid":317911,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cbd9f5e3cc1b87ee610d06c334d4d36b596c2f6","tid":317911,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1db93fb72c21ab7a1d844caab55b5c7fba66be83","tid":317911,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"支那人好人好姐怕乜野日本皇軍"},{"pid":"380a0026d64e53cf43bb94e389cf1e690cdb713c","tid":317911,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"問題ai呢樣野係支那一定會大推<br />\n令到外國都好想入中國分market"},{"pid":"18621d2e6370ecbf331f040f0b8e14e35253affd","tid":317911,"uid":48705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以預計到<br />\n將來最貴既野<br />\n唔係黃金唔係鑽石唔係豪宅<br />\n而係私隱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁住森林既人啲data味好值錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndata有咩味？酸味定甜味？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">味你老母</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f2ce6de3ec0a49188615546224822c3d8c9b40","tid":317911,"uid":58604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"呢個post 都有好多弱智仔data<br />\n今次fat fat了"},{"pid":"6304f974e4ef13de24b2182c6fa848f1b6645bb5","tid":317911,"uid":39846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實淘寶idea 幾好，省返請人既錢，令貨物格價更平，順便可以炒晒班廢老，廢中！高人工又效率低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先依個唔係淘寶idea 黎，什至唔算係一個idea.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果運行成功要炒嘅唔只會係超市嘅收銀。<br />\n個market 可以自動check,少左咩貨，幾時落order. Warehouses收到資料，利用algorithm 會自動向工廠訂貨。<br />\n工廠翻貨後按指求放係指定存放嘅area，warehouses 再分類比唔同目的地嘅門市。<br />\n<br />\n依&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;係咪少左啲嘢？係！少左人，以上過程可以係冇人參與！！ 只要warehouses 同 supermarket 嘅上落貨分類set 得好，淨係要兩三個貨車嘅司機上落貨，fill 貨已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原事實上，啲司機將來一定可以用auto pilot 代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而因為成個流程都係用algorithm 分流嘅，盤數ai 先最清楚，咁仲要accountant 做乜？炒埋<br />\n反正都淨係要幾個人黎睇住個system 就得，咁外判埋比外面啲service providers 啦。公司都冇員工，hr 都冇用啦。<br />\n<br />\n成個mid level 同 entry level 係可以完全被淘汰嘅，爽！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62c63c6092a5e3c2d8ca27659d79bd0c1330f0