,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T23:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先依個唔係淘寶idea 黎，什至唔算係一個idea.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果運行成功要炒嘅唔只會係超市嘅收銀。<br />\n個market 可以自動check,少左咩貨，幾時落order. Warehouses收到資料，利用algorithm 會自動向工廠訂貨。<br />\n工廠翻貨後按指求放係指定存放嘅area，warehouses 再分類比唔同目的地嘅門市。<br />\n<br />\n依&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;係咪少左啲嘢？係！少左人，以上過程可以係冇人參與！！ 只要warehouses 同 supermarket 嘅上落貨分類set 得好，淨係要兩三個貨車嘅司機上落貨，fill 貨已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原事實上，啲司機將來一定可以用auto pilot 代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而因為成個流程都係用algorithm 分流嘅，盤數ai 先最清楚，咁仲要accountant 做乜？炒埋<br />\n反正都淨係要幾個人黎睇住個system 就得，咁外判埋比外面啲service providers 啦。公司都冇員工，hr 都冇用啦。<br />\n<br />\n成個mid level 同 entry level 係可以完全被淘汰嘅，爽！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比到機器replace到既 仲唔撚係值得比人replace?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁，低下階層點算？人道毀滅？<br />\n定好北京摺疊咁永世隔絕？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都話可以做工廠包裝同運輸工人囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Human Resources 去做工廠妹，會計師去做運輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打你真係天真得可愛，寫一個ai 去分類易啲定，定寫一個固定嘅program 做packing 易啲? 心照啦，仲有得你包咩。<br />\n依家 cola 仲有包裝工有一部份係岀於 society responsibility 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實人唔做重複性工作，仲有好多用腦既野可以做！驚比人淘汰果班，通常都無腦！淨係識返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱呀，我講黎講去就係講無腦，能力又低嗰班，咁係咪要人道毀滅佢哋？<br />\n要用乜準側去judge?<br />\n要小心啲去judge 喎，因為終有一日會到ai 黎judge你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實會唔會係你對ai 太少了解？而又太高估自已？根本冇任何嘢ai 會比人差，even 藝術創作，用algorithm 一樣可以做到。只要你可以將受歡迎嘅elements break down, 佢一樣可以create 受歡迎嘅作品岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAi 識唔識拍AV ? Ai 使唔使食飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Ai 會唔會死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實如果機械人，仲未廣泛使用的話，有好多野都係仲需要人去做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> AI 只係用黎做啲重複性工作己經夠！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你啲問題想問乜呀？<br />\nArtificial intelligence 同機械人兩樣嘢黎喎。<br />\n你講黎講去都講唔岀點解決例技術嘅低下階層生活問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係識得話某一班人要比淘汰，太武斷下嘛？"},{"pid":"59eed43a9dfc7c489fac738e92606758d7ef86e1","tid":317911,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:11:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12cda1f454f42f43ebbb0317c444915b8a795fd3","tid":317911,"uid":60153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}